## Overview

Magic in Flow RPG uses a unified casting framework where the same spell produces different effects based on your casting attribute. Every spell can be cast using Mind, Awareness, Will, or Presence + Sorcery, each providing unique benefits.

**Casting Roll:** 2d6 + [Chosen Attribute] + Sorcery

### The Four Casting Approaches

- **Mind + Sorcery:** Precision, control, avoiding allies
- **Awareness + Sorcery:** Maximum damage, sensing weaknesses
- **Will + Sorcery:** Cast at negative Flow, persistence
- **Presence + Sorcery:** Social effects, fear/inspiration

